description:
Elmo loves
his fuzzy, blue blanket, and would never let anything happen to it. A tug-of-war with his friend Zoe sends his blanket to a faraway land, and Elmo is in hot pursuit. Facing life without his cherished blanket, Elmo musters all of his courage and heads off on an action-packed rescue mission that plunges him into Grouchland.
